1.title: Goblin Quest: The Trojan Goat
1.plot: Simon, Lewis, Sjin and Tom send a bunch of Goblins to fail spectacularly at easy tasks.

2.title: Goblin Quest: Double Danger Double Down
2.plot: The Goblins learn to drive and escape the camp.

3.title: Goblin Quest: FIRE! (Final)
3.plot: Fire. Fire Everywhere. You name it, it's probably on fire.

1.title: Adventurers Assemble
1.plot: An unlikely ban of heroes find themselves plunged into a fantasy world of excitement, treasure, loot, busty wenches, ale, goblins, dwarves, and creepy things that wriggle in the darkness.

2.title: Owl Tassels
2.plot: The adventure begins with the party reaching the small hillside town of Wook and immediately getting sidetracked.

3.title: Jambawok Whispers
3.plot: While pondering their next move in Shafties bar, the heroes meet a strange character and hear some unsettling rumors.

4.title: Rubbish Dump
4.plot: It's a lovely morning in Wook, and the adventurers attempt to gear themselves up before continuing on.

5.title: Crazy Doors
5.plot: Armed to the teeth, the heroes take their first steps into the dungeon and begin to battle its denizens.

6.title: Tomb Raiders
6.plot: Team awesome delve deeper into the dungeon, and begin working to unravel its mysteries.

7.title: Critical Fail
7.plot: Team awesome delve deeper into the dungeon, and begin working to unravel its mysteries.

8.title: Flaming Sword
8.plot: Team awesome delve deeper into the dungeon, and begin working to unravel its mysteries.

9.title: Eat Of My Pie
9.plot: Team awesome delve deeper into the dungeon, and begin working to unravel its mysteries.

10.title: Gelatinous Cube
10.plot: The mysteries of the dungeon have been revealed, and the heroes find themselves fighting for their lives in the dank and dark.

1.title: A New Rim
1.plot: Strap in for a brand new YogsQuest - in space. With Sips at the helm, Duncan as the captain, Sjin as the muscle, and Simon doing the cleaning, there is nothing that can stop them from flying into an adventure of galactic proportions.

2.title: Off The Starboard Bow
2.plot: The adventure gets under way with the discovery of a mysterious ship off the starboard bow. The crew of the Rim Hopper now have to decide what their best course of action is and if they have the skills to pull off their daring plan.

3.title: The Other Ship
3.plot: The crew venture deep into the mysterious ship. It's pitch black on board and the walls are caked in a slick, slimy substance. Is there anyone alive on-board? Are there creatures lurking in the shadows?

4.title: We're Not Alone
4.plot: The guys come face-to-face with the horrific beasts that are running riot in this blood-soaked ship. Fingers crossed our heroes have the intestinal fortitude to face off against these fearsome beasts.

5.title: Takedown!
5.plot: The barrage of enemies isn't over yet, Sjin has to muster all his mighty strength to tackle the biggest monster of them all, a beast that resembles a mess of tentacles covering an inside out bear.

6.title: Epic Maneuver
6.plot: The battle with the beasts continues deep in the heart of the alien ship. When the crew find themselves in a dire situation they turn to their fearless hairdresser/pilot and he attempts one of his most daring moves to date.

7.title: The Fuzzykin
7.plot: After coming across the fuzzykin in the med bay, our heroes attempt to figure out why such a cute and fuzzy little fella is on a ship full of hideous flesh beasts and what they can do to help.

8.title: Bye Bye Blueballs
8.plot: Now the team must make a daring escape from the alien ship and venture back out into open space to make it back to the rust bucket they call home, The Rim Hopper.

9.title: Fat Stan's Diner
9.plot: The crew of the Rim Hopper arrive at Fat Stan's space truck stop, this place looks rough, they'll have to have their wits about them as they explore this wretched hive of scum and villainy.

10.title: Wanted Men
10.plot: With their bellies full of Fat Stan's grub, the crew receives some unwelcome news from an old friend.

11.title: Space Love
11.plot: The destruction of the diner commences with an all out fire fight but amid the chaos our old love machine Sips spies a certain somebody he could work his magic on.

12.title: Let's Blow This Joint
12.plot: The guys decide their best move is to abandon the diner and head for the stars. Close behind them is something familiar, the giant bleep on the radar is back.

13.title: Cubonians
13.plot: Cruising through space the guys recover from their ordeal at Fat Stan's, but their relaxation doesn't last long when a new enemy approaches to bombard their vulnerable ship.

14.title: Jackpot
14.plot: The boys are still tangled up in a Cubonian attack. With defeat knocking at their door, Simon's quick thinking and super welding skills come in useful when adding some much needed upgrades to his rusty robot body.

15.title: Crime Planet
15.plot: Our adventure continues with us exploring a wretched hive of scum and villainy, a lawless planet populated by the toughest criminals in the galaxy.

16.title: Mysterious Package
16.plot: Down on the crime planet the gang bump into a frantic stranger who hands Duncan a mysterious brown bag.

17.title: Pet Store
17.plot: The gang explore what the crime planet has to offer with its many stores and attractions, one such place being the pet store where Sips finds a new friend.

18.title: Wheels
18.plot: Sjin needs some healing and the only person in town qualified to help is Dr Butcher. Everything seems to be going swimmingly until Sjin discovers the doc's method of healing him.

19.title: Master Blasters
19.plot: The gang round off their trip to the crime planet with a quick stop at the weapons shop, Master Blasters, where they get tooled up and kitted out with upgrades.

20.title: The Gang
20.plot: The gang are forced to leave the crime planet early when something approaches from the wilds of space, but with the gang growing bigger their hopes are high that they can take down whatever it is that's seeking them.

21.title: Thaddeus Tripp
21.plot: It's time for the gang to find out what this gold artifact is for and whether it was worth dragging it around with them this whole adventure. Fir this we they find the rhino man, Thaddeus Tripp.

22.title: The Goroloth
22.plot: The gang face the creature that has been hunting them the entire adventure, the planet-sized Goroloth. They must now gather everything they've learned and take down this creature that threatens the entire galaxy.

23.title: Super Simon
23.plot: The fight in the brain chamber continues. The gang pushed to the brink when Duncan is brought to his knees mid-fight, but Simon has a secret weapon up his metallic sleeve that even he didn't know about.

24.title: The Final Stand
24.plot: The adventure comes to an end as the gang fight off the hordes of beasts that surround the brain of the monstrous Goroloth. All they have to do now is put the gold thing in the brain and everything will be fine - right?

1.title: Zombie Bite
1.plot: YogsQuest is back and this time they're surviving the zombie apocalypse. Join Sips, Sjin, Duncan, and a Trott on this epic quest through the zombie wasteland where weird characters and hilarious adventure await.

2.title: Water Blast
2.plot: Sjin manages to get on the hose and cause chaos with his powerful water blast.

3.title: Zombie Whisperer
3.plot: The group meet a very strange man who seems to have control over zombies. What's his secret?

4.title: Prisoners
4.plot: The group are chained up in a shed, awaiting their fate. They must think of a plan before it is too late.

5.title: Zombie Sips
5.plot: Sips has turned into a zombie, and now the group are trapped in the gas station with the flesh-eating, undead bastard.

6.title: Barterland
6.plot: The new crew stumble into the local shop to try and get a good deal on some premium loot.

7.title: The Lab
7.plot: The group enter the mysterious lab. What will they find inside?

8.title: Muscle Men
8.plot: The group meet a muscle-man science guy who they hope has the solution to all of their zombie problems.

9.title: Boy Scouts
9.plot: The group come across a boy scout in the road. They're not sure if they should trust this kid, but then again, what's the worst that could happen?

10.title: Bear Pit
10.plot: The Boy Scouts have captured the group and their leader, Timmy, reveals his final challenge - The Bear Pit.

11.title: Fort Victory
11.plot: The group have finally made it to Fort Victory. Now all they have to do is get inside.

12.title: Familiar Faces
12.plot: This is it, the journey ends here. Can the group get on the helicopter before it leaves? Get ready for a nail biting and hilarious finale.

1.title: Edge of the Empire Part I #1: A New Hope-Less Team
1.plot: Join Lewis, Simon, Sjin, and Harry on an adventure in Star Wars Edge of the Empire DnD. Tom is the Dungeon Master and has much planned for the band of mercenaries.

2.title: Edge of the Empire Part I #2: Lobo The Hutt
2.plot: Join Lewis, Simon, Sjin, and Harry on an adventure in Stars Wars Edge of the Empire DnD. Tom is the Dungeon Master and has much planned for our band of mercenaries. Today they meet with LoBo The Hutt.

3.title: Edge of the Empire Part I #3: Catch A Ride!
3.plot: The team must secure a ride from Blanks the mechanic.

4.title: Edge of the Empire Part I #4: The Town of Krayt Drop
4.plot: The team arrives at the town of Krayt Drop.

5.title: Edge of the Empire Part I #5: The Hangover
5.plot: After a night of heavy drinking at Spunky's bar, the team moves forward with their mission.

6.title: Edge of the Empire Part I #6: Sullustan Spritzing
6.plot: The team meet a sleepy Sullustan, and they just can't stop messing with him.

7.title: Edge of the Empire Part I #7: The Bank Manager
7.plot: Finally making it to the bank, the team are met with a surprising bank manager.

8.title: Edge of the Empire: Searching For Answers
8.plot: After casing the joint, the team now looks for a way into the vault.

9.title: Edge of the Empire Part I #9: The Bank Job
9.plot: After a rocky start, the team has a plan to rob the bank.

10.title: Edge of the Empire Part I #10: The Sheriff of Krayt Drop
10.plot: As the team escapes, they're confronted by someone they didn't expect to see.

11.title: Edge of the Empire Part I #11: Into the Sunset
11.plot: After their decisive battle, an unexpected ally swoops in to aid the team's escape.

12.title: Edge of the Empire Part II #1: Back to the Crime Scene
12.plot: Lost in the desert, the guys are hitching a ride back to the crime scene.

13.title: Edge of the Empire Part II #2: Imperial Checkpoint
13.plot: Stealing another speeder, the guys try to get through an imperial checkpoint.

14.title: Edge of the Empire Part II #3: The Rusty Droid
14.plot: A brawl with a trucker, another checkpoint and, finally, entry into Mos Crucas.

15.title: Edge of the Empire Part II #4: Enter the Battleground!
15.plot: Inside the Rusty Droid the gang find a way to make a quick buck.

16.title: Edge of the Empire Part II #5: Paint the Arena Brown
16.plot: Geycukk is facing off against Badu Ba Bagu in the battle arena. It's gonna get dirty.

17.title: Edge of the Empire Part III #1: Hyper Smut
17.plot: After a dirty fight, the guys are mugging an old lady and heading off for a spot of shopping.

18.title: Edge of the Empire Part III #2: Ameebo, Imperial Police
18.plot: Heading deeper into Mos Cruces, the guys are finally following the address Rusty gave them.

19.title: Edge of the Empire Part III #3: Stealthy Drick's Dirty Tricks
19.plot: The gang finally find Johnny Scrambles, but it seems he's a little busy being arrested.

20.title: Edge of the Empire Part III #4: Worker Strike
20.plot: Deep inside Whisper Base, the gang get jobs and make friends with some conspiring workers.

21.title: Edge of the Empire Part IV #1: Battle of Whisper Base
21.plot: Ameebo, Geycukk, Drick and IG-04 have found themselves in the middle of a full blown war between the Empire and the Worker Resistance.

22.title: Edge of the Empire Part IV #2: The Kill Crazies
22.plot: Ameebo is in a bad way as the gang head deeper into Whisper Base.

23.title: Edge of the Empire Part IV #3: Prisoner Chain
23.plot: Deep inside Whisper Base the guys finally make it to the prison and, hopefully, Johnny Scrambles.

24.title: Edge of the Empire Part IV #4: A Flight To Remember
24.plot: The gang manage to convince a whole host of people to join them on their flight out of Whisper Base.

25.title: Edge of the Empire Part V #1: The Ameebo Manoeuvre
25.plot: Back in their Lambda Shuttle, the guys are evading Imperial Fighters.

26.title: Edge of the Empire Part V #2: Tusken Assault
26.plot: After landing their ship in the middle of The Fangs, the guys are getting assaulted by Tusken Raiders.

27.title: Edge of the Empire Part V #3: Rando Smegstar
27.plot: Breaking into the Pod Racing HQ, the gang meet a kind old man with a big old gun.

28.title: Edge of the Empire Part V #4: Race Against Time
28.plot: The gang left the money (and Drick) behind in a hoard of Sand People. Can they save the money (and Drick), get back to Lobo in time and finally repay their debt?

29.title: Edge of the Empire Part VI #1: When Things Go South
29.plot: After settling their debt, the gang are approached by a desperate man hoping for vengeance against some bandits.

30.title: Edge of the Empire Part VI #2: Black Fang Gang
30.plot: The guys head to the drop point to find who is threatening Boatman's mother and discover the literary gang behind all of this.

31.title: Edge of the Empire Part VI #3: Slam Poetry
31.plot: The guys have prepared some poetry to impress the Black Fang Gang. It goes about as well as expected.

32.title: Edge of the Empire Part VI #4: Got The Hots
32.plot: After their attempts at poetry the guys fall into the debt of the Black Fang Gang. Guess they've got another mission to do.

1.title: Call of Cthulhu: The Carrington Estate
1.plot: The Dice Boys are back for another terrifying adventure in the Lovecraftian Call of Cthulhu D&D Adventure. A PI, a Professor, a Journalist and a Mobster are heading up to the Carrington Estate to investigate a broken statue.

2.title: Call of Cthulhu: The Wrong Path
2.plot: Investigating what little leads they have on their strange egg-rocks, the gang are struggling with an impasse.

3.title: Call of Cthulhu: Mysterious Murders
3.plot: Grim tidings as the investigators arrive back at Carrington Estate. Finally, some clues that will lead to those missing people. Grizwald has some important questions for them, after all.

4.title: Call of Cthulhu: To the Library!
4.plot: Interviews and breadcrumbs take the crew on a hunt for a book that should reveal more about the monster.

5.title: Call of Cthulhu: Very Unlucky Boy
5.plot: Back for another stream the gang are back to meet and old friend of Crystal's.

6.title: Call of Cthulhu: We Belive
6.plot: We're meeting up with a guy who knows a lot about the Marsh Wizard.

7.title: Call of Cthulhu: Marsh Marauders
7.plot: Professor Grizwald is revealing a lot about himself today as the group slog through the dark, dank and mysterious marsh.

8.title: Call of Cthulhu: Beast Summoner Grizwald
8.plot: In the final episode of our Call of Cthuhlu series the investigators find a unique way to deal with the beast terrorizing the Carrington Estate.

1.title: A Star Wars Story: The Adventure Begins!
1.plot: Unlikely allies Lewis, Sips, Turps and Harry begin their adventure across the galaxy, meeting crazy characters and battling crazier aliens all under the control of evil Game Master Tom.

2.title: A Star Wars Story: Mission Accepted
2.plot: The gang are having trouble with a dog but Zin Zin has a dangerous mission ready for them.

3.title: A Star Wars Story: The Chase Is On!
3.plot: A wily eavesdropper working for one of Ameebo's many rivals heard the entire plan. The chase is on.

4.title: A Star Wars Story: Making a Come Back
4.plot: Ameebo's ship has been tagged with a tracker so the guys come up with a plan to throw him off the scent using an Imperial Starship.

5.title: A Star Wars Story: Setting Course for Vorlok-9
5.plot: After successfully evading Derek and tricking Biro the gang jump into Bernadette and set a course for the dangerous Vorlok-9.

6.title: A Star Wars Story: Operation: Save Pod
6.plot: Crash landed on the jungle planet of Vorlok-9 the guys need to get out of the burning wreckage of Bernadette.

7.title: A Star Wars Story: Fighting for Food
7.plot: On the trail of the crashed ship and hungrier than ever the gang resort to Nerf Punching to get some food.

8.title: A Star Wars Story: Blood Eagles!
8.plot: Rooting around Derek's crashed ship the gang make a camp and get attacked by some vicious Blood Eagles.

9.title: A Star Wars Story: A Night In The Jungle
9.plot: The gang spend a night in the dark and dangerous jungle.

10.title: A Star Wars Story: The Town of Two Suns
10.plot: Two team arrive in a town inhabited entirely by robots who immediately put them to work.

11.title: A Star Wars Story: Pompo's Diner
11.plot: The gang have to role-play their jobs as the Robots head in to Pompo's diner for some dinner.

12.title: A Star Wars Story: There's Been A Murder!
12.plot: The boys try everything to get into the vault and find Reefmax while the town investigate the brutal murder of Pompo.

13.title: A Star Wars Story: Changing Hats
13.plot: Court is in session for the murder of Pompo and the town change their jobs.

14.title: A Star Wars Story: Reefmax
14.plot: The gang get their new jobs and finally meet the legendary Reefmax.

15.title: A Star Wars Story: Goodbye, Two Suns
15.plot: The guys say their farewells to Two Suns as they try to get off this planet with the Zarpeen Gem.

16.title: A Star Wars Story: A Rock and a Hard Place
16.plot: In the final episode the gang face a horde of enemies as they escape from the planet with their prize.

1.title: Call of Cthulhu: Gone Missing
1.plot: John Steel and his friends are back to investigate a series of disappearances in this 1920s Lovecraftian horror.

2.title: Call of Cthulhu: The PP Investigation
2.plot: The investigation into the missing people goes off course when Horatio Pendragon takes an interest in some wild Parsnips.

3.title: Call of Cthulhu: From Strange to Stranger
3.plot: Meeting some of the residents the gang find that things are going from strange to stranger.

4.title: Call of Cthulhu: A Night with the Jarvies
4.plot: The gang spend a night with the Jarvies and investigate the Professor's last known location.

5.title: Call of Cthulhu: Farmyard Rumble!
5.plot: It's a very eventful night for the group in Jarvies farm.

6.title: Call of Cthulhu: What Lies Beneath
6.plot: Things are getting sinister when the boys carry out an autopsy of a pig, find an abandoned dig site and Henry Rhodes' destroyed camp.

7.title: Call of Cthulhu: The Thing in the Water
7.plot: The team find a floating "thing" in the water and begin investigating the Comitis.

8.title: Call of Cthulhu: The Melting Man
8.plot: The gang find something deeply disturbing deep inside Comitis farm.

9.title: Call of Cthulhu: Into the Caves
9.plot: Henry wants us to head into a deep, dark and scary cave.

10.title: Call of Cthulhu: Mother
10.plot: Mother's here. It's time to end this mystery once and for all.

1.title: Rise of a Civilisation: Planting the Seed
1.plot: Simon, Tom, Ben and Harry are back to tell the story of the Rise of a Civilisation.

2.title: Rise of a Civilisation: The God Train
2.plot: Salizmund has captured Zardon the Many-Legged to power his God Train. How will he get away with it?

3.title: Rise of a Civilisation: Murder on the Trans-Continent Express
3.plot: There's been a murder on the Trans-Continent Express. Who's the victim and, most importantly, who's the culprit?

4.title: Rise of a Civilisation: Council of the Gods
4.plot: Hotep, King (or God) of Gods, is being punished for deceiving thousands of people.

5.title: Rise of a Civilisation: Founding of the Godkillers
5.plot: We conclude Snazrazz Mazzlejazz's small claims God-Court and discover the humble beginnings of the Godkillers.

6.title: Rise of a Civilisation: Death of the Gods
6.plot: The final turn brings a new focus, and Simon decides to pinpoint the Death of the Gods.

1.title: Call of Cthulhu: Meet the Family
1.plot: Nick Steele is sending suspicious letters from Danvers State Hospital. The family jump in to investigate.

2.title: Call of Cthulhu: A Cunning Plan
2.plot: The gang make plans to get into Danver's State Hospital. Costumes, disguises and forged documents aplenty.

3.title: Call of Cthulhu: The Danvers Tour
3.plot: The gang, equipped with a Murder Bag and Guns, take a tour of Danver's State Hospital.

4.title: Call of Cthulhu: Burger and Steak
4.plot: After a close call the gang head off for a recap on everything they've seen so far.

5.title: Call of Cthulhu: Knife Salesmen
5.plot: The boys investigate Dr. Burger's old home and terrorize and old woman.

6.title: Call of Cthulhu: History Boys
6.plot: The team head to City Hall to check out the history of the mysterious Danver's State Hospital.

7.title: Call of Cthulhu: The Grand Dynamite Heist
7.plot: The gang break into a mine to steal some dynamite. It doesn't go to plan.

8.title: Call of Cthulhu: Making Plans
8.plot: Back at Herman's the team make plans to break into Danver's State Hospital.

9.title: Call of Cthulhu: A Way In
9.plot: The boys have a plan to break into Danver's State. Let's see if it goes to plan.

10.title: Call of Cthulhu: The Ritual
10.plot: The ritual has begun, Nick Steele's life is at stake.

11.title: Call of Cthulhu: The Blood God
11.plot: A giant serpent, a horde of madmen, a ticking time bomb and more threaten the team in the final episode of YogsQuest - Call of Cthulhu.

1.title: Microscope - A New Earth: The Hunt for N'Earth
1.plot: Tom, Simon, Ben and Lewis create a brand new universe. Earth is doomed and humanity embarks on a journey to find a New Earth - N'Earth.

2.title: Microscope - A New Earth: Bogulon 9
2.plot: Ben introduces the Fungicide of Bogulon 9.

3.title: Microscope - A New Earth: Fungicide Debate
3.plot: Hearings take place to determine the fate of Bogulon 9.

4.title: Microscope - A New Earth: Zarblep's Grand Booty
4.plot: The gang look deep into Zarblep's grand booty.

5.title: Microscope - A New Earth: Hyper Coronation
5.plot: It's time for J''eff's Hyper Coronation. Unfortunately, other people want to take that title off him.

6.title: Microscope - A New Earth: Planetary Top Gun
6.plot: President Wang needs convincing while the human race escape on their planet-ships.

7.title: Microscope - A New Earth: Last Pass (Final)
7.plot: The gang wrap up the New Earth time-line with a final pass,
